{"tid":968670,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"江嘉敏為男友整白色忌廉生日蛋糕","createTime":"2019-01-04T11:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T12:10:04.000Z","uid":160973,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"84c16234042645829239da454ef2fdda2e14be28","tid":968670,"uid":160973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T11:54:52.000Z","msg":"從片段片可見，嘉敏超用心調配材料和裝飾蛋糕，加上獨角獸裝飾和馬卡龍。粉藍色的蛋糕除了充滿少女心，還充滿濃濃愛意。唔少網民看畢短片都大讚她的蛋糕賣相精美。不過，貪吃的嘉敏製作途中忍不住偷食，被朋友問：「這位同學在做什麼？」拿着一大盤忌廉的嘉敏偷偷舔吃忌廉，露出滿足的表情。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2VuuMTN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2VuuMTN&d=SZHOSRZOfqO07P%2BUh5c00wCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=f6bd64ce\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2VuuMTN</a>"},{"pid":"5df56f6fdfe0e60af09af1b67ae282ecca2bbef0","tid":968670,"uid":6842,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T11:55:52.000Z","msg":"喂呀！好sweet呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a883b1cae74d947af6aaa1552afd30879b92abc","tid":968670,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T11:59:54.000Z","msg":"喂也"},{"pid":"38612edf54acfef0f8ed76b3503ec67b0189b7f8","tid":968670,"uid":46587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T12:01:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拿着一大盤忌廉的嘉敏偷偷舔吃忌廉，<span style=\"color: red;\">露出滿足的表情</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2VuuMTN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2VuuMTN&d=SZHOSRZOfqO07P%2BUh5c00wCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=f6bd64ce\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2VuuMTN</a></blockquote><br />\n平時食左幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef7d6fcabf540ebf16f6566465d648350026291","tid":968670,"uid":35930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T12:06:41.000Z","msg":"俾男友整個忌廉批好過啦"},{"pid":"49e15b55825172f4fd45def363c8f1f952566c66","tid":968670,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":